### About the release process automation

The release process automation provides slash commands on Release Issues:
- `/create-snapshot` — create a release snapshot with mechanical transformations
- `/discard-snapshot` — discard a snapshot and return to planned state
- `/delete-draft` — delete a draft release
- `/publish-release --confirm <tag>` — publish the release

Release Issues are created automatically when `release-plan.yaml` is updated on main.
Updates to `release-plan.yaml` are done via PRs that change only this file.

